Text: This is one of the best albums of Incubus. Don't stop seeding ;p This torrent is great!

Great album, marred by the brutal 96 kbps bitrate. Seriously, it sounds terrible. I mean sure, you want to make the file size as small as possible, but you have to strike a compromise...

On a positive note, no viruses and no extra crap. However, 'extra crap' also appears to apply to album art on this one, which is significantly absent.
